/* plugins common to all models -- trimmed to lastfm_scrobbler plus five
 * more that turned out to be load-bearing for other features, not just
 * standalone utilities, so they're staying:
 *   - playing_time.c: apps/onplay.c's "Playing Time" current-playlist menu
 *     item plugin_load()s this directly; without it that item silently
 *     fails to open.
 *   - db_folder_select.c: apps/menus/settings_menu.c's "Directories to
 *     Scan" database setting and the AUTORESUME_NEXTTRACK_CUSTOM folder
 *     picker both plugin_load() this directly; without it those two
 *     settings silently fail to open.
 *   - view_text.c: apps/screens.c's Track Info screen opens this to show
 *     a long field (e.g. file path/comment) in a scrollable full-text
 *     view.
 *   - properties.c: apps/onplay.c's properties_item/track_info_item menu
 *     entries and the HOTKEY_PROPERTIES hotkey all load this via
 *     viewers.config's "*,properties,-" mapping; without it, File
 *     Properties/Track Info silently fail to open.
 *   - credits.c: apps/menus/main_menu.c's show_credits() does fall back
 *     to a plain info screen if this is missing, so it's not load-bearing
 *     the same way, but keeping it anyway.
 * lastfm_scrobbler_viewer.c (lastfm_scrobbler's "View Playback Log"
 * companion) removed entirely -- buggy, not worth keeping; the menu item
 * and view_playback_log() that called it are gone from lastfm_scrobbler.c
 * too, not just this listing.
 * Everything else previously here (games, demos, emulators, remaining
 * viewers/utilities only ever reachable through the generic Plugins
 * browser) has been removed. main_menu_config.c and pictureflow.c
 * specifically: both superseded by core ports (apps/menus/
 * main_menu_config.c, apps/gui/album_covers.c) earlier this fork -- not
 * part of this trim, just finally deleted as dead weight now that this
 * file was being edited anyway.
 * keyremap.c removed too: it was only ever reachable through the generic
 * Plugins browser, same as the games/demos/emulators above -- no core
 * call site ever plugin_load()ed it directly. */
#ifdef HAVE_TAGCACHE
db_folder_select.c
#endif
credits.c
lastfm_scrobbler.c
playing_time.c
properties.c
view_text.c
